oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Memphis City Soccer Champions, 1925
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Athletes; Soccer; Soccer players
oai_dc:dc.dc:description:
The Soccer Cup was presented by the U.S. Football Association for the promotion of school and junior soccer to the Christian Brothers College team in 1925.
The photo includes Howard Mayer, Larry Lee, Jack Guinee, Tom Robinson, and Tic Manigan; others, unknown.
